     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="3"/>
   <head>Vpon the Author.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>THryse happie <hi>Abria,</hi> to whose lasting Fame,</l>
      <l>Right valiant <hi>Mercers</hi> Muse hath vndergone:</l>
      <l>To gild, in rich encomiums each mans name,</l>
      <l>Like <hi>Mars,</hi> and <hi>Maro,</hi> both combynd in one,</l>
      <l>For to your praise what hee hath pend in word,</l>
      <l>Hee bravely vowes for to maintaine by sword.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>W. Dow.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
